> Configuration -> Preferences -> Wrapping:
> 
> "	[x] Auto wrapping
> 	[ ] Wrap quotation
> 	[ ] Wrap pasted text
> 
> Wrap messages at [..] characters"
> 
> 
> Then use the "Insert File" button or (xclip < mypatch.diff && middle
> mouse button).
